Author: itcomeswithatoy
Text: i know im only saying what you already know deep down but sometimes it helps to hear it from somebody else: you didn’t gain any weight. you are at a deficit. your progress is safe, even if you don’t feel like that’s true, please try to say to yourself whenever your ed tries to tear you down.  even if you hadn’t undereaten, you are not greedy. no matter how much you eat or restrict or exercise, you are always deserving care and happiness. of course, that’s easier said than done. but please please take care of yourself.
